DLW-SPUN · the full weave of Beltur

who   : The mongrel mage, a hunted gray who wields both order and chaos at once.
what  : The mongrel mage — wields BOTH order and chaos.
where : Gallos to Elparta — The Mongrel Mage, Outcasts of Order, The Mage-Fire War.
why   : Refuses to be only one thing, and is hunted for it.
when  : The early age of Candar's warring city-states — The Mongrel Mage through The Mage-Fire War.
how   : Holds the two forces in tension where others can hold but one.

class : The Gray · those who hold both
